    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i just feel like 5mg is a lot for someone as active as me now. i've read that some people can maintain their level on much lower doses if they lead a healthy lifestyle. if i just started tapering down slowly on my own, like 2mg instead of 5mg, would that be a safe way to see if i still need the full amount?",
